{"tid":553642,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"喺香港，以平民及中產階層黎講，邊區最好住，邊區最唔好住？","createTime":"2018-02-07T16:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-09T08:42:29.000Z","uid":155084,"like":8,"dislike":114,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"c2402b45877c393137877ce9d7bf2f917aa3c111","tid":553642,"uid":155084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:14:09.000Z","msg":"最好住：慈雲山<br />\n<br />\n慈雲山<br />\n論食：大把野食，小店又有，連鎖野又有，深夜都有野食。<br />\n<br />\n論交通：深夜都好幾架紅頂小巴，慈雲山雖無地鐵站，但落黃大仙或鑽石山非常方便，可以接受。<br />\n<br />\n紅頂小巴：旺角（24小時）、銅鑼灣、佐敦道、荃灣、青山道（早上）<br />\n綠頂小巴：九龍塘、黃大仙、鑽石山、新蒲崗、竹園<br />\n<br />\n娛樂設施：體育館、公園、足球場、籃球場、單車場 ...<br />\n<br />\n生活質素：背山，空氣還不錯。物價有平有中等，唔會太貴。<br />\n<br />\n~ <br />\n<br />\n最唔好住 ... 諗唔到。大家有乜想法？"},{"pid":"d8a17de94489fbead0362394d1dd74ddfb26f5f5","tid":553642,"uid":141475,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:14:47.000Z","msg":"平民一定係屯門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29cbd23362ca20ed2e7354cc94e27c44a48a41f9","tid":553642,"uid":129039,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d8a17de94489fbead0362394d1dd74ddfb26f5f5","tid":553642,"uid":141475,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:14:47.000Z","msg":"平民一定係屯門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8b85a76644e06af434dabe9919f06fbc40532de","tid":553642,"uid":48276,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"淨係上山落山都要3.8$一程<br />\n小數怕長計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda092e4cfcec3f5c4412bbbddf7344915c81c99","tid":553642,"uid":11254,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d8a17de94489fbead0362394d1dd74ddfb26f5f5","tid":553642,"uid":141475,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T16:14:47.000Z","msg":"平民一定係屯門