7f93c02caffa5240bb949108e269","tid":553642,"uid":105275,"like":14,"dislike":5,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T17:30:41.000Z","msg":"中產住沙田我覺得最好"},{"pid":"352761f021963493c0766b0a31c2b3ab0ff98d58","tid":553642,"uid":2679,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"平民黃大仙 石硤尾公屋啦<br />\n少蝗少蝻 廢老區極少後生<br />\n就算有新移民 市區中學都會學識講廣東話<br />\n交通方便 搭一兩個站就已經九龍塘<br />\n又有沙中線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幾十條巴士線係大路 <br />\n行出荔枝角道/龍翔道乜車都有<br />\n<br />\n除左去啲大西北同大東北<br />\n搭去港九新界的士最多一百幾十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c699c2ffb9fe4f0a9ad90896bfc6057cc4a5a1","tid":553642,"uid":2679,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"中產最好我覺得紅磡幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旺中帶靜 玩完搭的士翻屋企都係幾十蚊有找<br />\n野食有幾條街 又有地鐵站 火車站<br />\n<br />\n住沙田搭的士 夜晚當你CWB走<br />\n都要舊幾水先翻到去<br />\n住紅磡都係幾十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcaeb73f1a8a7f0d165e1865b4ded4067a8f29e2","tid":553642,"uid":129658,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:18:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中產最好我覺得紅磡幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n旺中帶靜 玩完搭的士翻屋企都係幾十蚊有找<br />\n野食有幾條街 又有地鐵站 火車站<br />\n<br />\n住沙田搭的士 夜晚當你CWB走<br />\n都要舊幾水先翻到去<br />\n住紅磡都係幾十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅磡/九龍城真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗親塞車塞到瀨哂屎就唔想入去"},{"pid":"2e573054153b107feaa86b9a49583f119cb00a6b","tid":553642,"uid":3501,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-07T18:27:35.000Z","msg":"唔會揀慈雲山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認同荃灣<br />\n同埋藍田都ok啊"},{"pid":"2e9ec4b8d9c4bcd199b650640cc192c2c879a2cd","tid":553642,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyT